2(1).40.10</biblScope> </bibl> (Epid., <date TEIform=\"date\">v B.C.</date>). </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n94677.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> as a military phrase, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπὶ σκέλος πάλιν χωρεῖν, ἀνάγειν</foreign>, retreat with the face towards the enemy, retire leisurely, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg015.perseus-grc1:1400\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1400</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:383\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">383</biblScope> </bibl>; cf. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πούς</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1:6b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.6b</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"3\" id=\"n94677.2\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατὰ σκέλος βαδίζειν</foreign>, of the lion and the camel, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">with the hind foot following the fore on the same side</tr_> (not crosswise), <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:498b:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ HA\">HA</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">498b7</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg014:629b:14\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">629b14</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n94677.3\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sens